ComicInfo.Title: Artificial Intelligence Part 1
ComicInfo.Series: G.I. Joe: A Real American Hero
ComicInfo.Summary: Artificial Intelligence Part 1: In Shazidar, Dusty and Cover Girl's team meets up with Airborne's squad as they escort the aid workers and children. The Joes rendezvous with Wild Bill in a C-130 but only two of their three vehicles can board, forcing Cover Girl to abandon a Chenowth full of C-4. When Green Morning rebels stop to collect the explosives, Joystick fires his last drone missile at them, detonating the explosives. Meanwhile in Kansas, Destro and Baroness fight their way out of the Revanche silo but Alpha 001 Prime follows them to the surface.
